snippet.title: Best VGM 236 - Castlevania II - The Silence of the Daylight
snippet.description:
Best VGM 340 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rhbGqHurV5I
Best VGM 1262 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dQRiJz_nEP8

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

NES
Castlevania II: Simon's Quest
The Silence of the Daylight (Town)
